title: Star Wars - Republic Commando [PC] [ENG] [FULL]
description:
INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS


1. Mount and Install Republic Commando.
2. Copy the crack file to: Star Wars Republic Commando\GameData\System and overwrite.
3. Done!



-==Game crashing issue==-



To prevent the game from crashing prior to playing the single player campaign go to:


OPTIONS > GRAPHICS and set BUMPMAPPING QUALITY to LOW.


Should run on Windows 7 and 8.


Enjoy & Please Seed!
